# Drawer Installation

You can [install Drawer package](https://www.nuget.org/packages/Skclusive.Material.Drawer/) by typing the below command in your terminal:

```csharp
dotnet add package Skclusive.Material.Drawer
```

Then, you can import it in your `_Imports.razor`.

```csharp
@using Skclusive.Material.Drawer
```

Then, you can render the style for this component it in your `Router.razor`.

```html
<DrawerStyle />
```

